Class Hash<T>

java.lang.Object
  ds.util.Hash<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collection<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>
public class Hash<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Collection<T>, Iterable<T>

This class implements the Collection interface using a hash table as the underlying storage structure.
